@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}



<div class="container privacy-policy">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>At the Joburg Maintenance Portal, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when using our platform.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Personal identification information (Name, email address, phone number, etc.)</li>
        <li>Details about maintenance requests you submit</li>
        <li>Technical data such as your IP address, browser type, and session information</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your personal data to provide and improve our services, such as processing your maintenance requests, notifying you of updates, and ensuring the smooth functioning of the portal.</p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access. However, please note that no online platform is entirely secure, and you should also take steps to safeguard your personal data.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to request access to or deletion of your personal information. For any concerns or requests, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@joburgmaintenance.gov.za">support@joburgmaintenance.gov.za</a>.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <div class="contact-info">
        <p>If you have any questions about our privacy practices, please contact us at:</p>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@joburgmaintenance.gov.za">privacy@joburgmaintenance.gov.za</a></p>
        <p>Phone: 0800-123-456</p>
    </div>
</div>
